(Corrects company name in first paragraph.)  Cnooc Ltd.’s $15.1 billion bid for
 Nexen Inc. (NXY)  would have significant implications and must be
judged to be in the long-term interest of the Canadian economy,
Prime Minister  Stephen Harper  said.  Harper made the comment to reporters in Cambridge Bay,
Nunavut.  To contact the reporter on this story:
